<br>
    The sad part is many people have grouped with Lancerblood and will vouch he’s a decent guy to group with at the same time though he was scamming people with Bagend.  He knows right from wrong, It was not an accident with these scams, he didn’t trip and fall and rip people off, it was pre-meditated and all he had to do was apologize and get out of it, well, not with me. All you people that want to forgive and forget, power to you, you’re a better person than I, but the next time Bagend/Lancerblood (or insert dumb @#%$ here) catches you grabbing your ankles, turn around and tell him “I forgive you” on his way to the bank.<br>
<br>
I do want to get something straight, I do not hate anybody in RL over a stupid game but I’m entitled to hate his or her actions while in the game. Please, no English majors grade my post; I’ve had a few beers and well…....... nm, grade the @#%$ out of it.<br>
