<br>
Secondly- <br>
Don't buy accounts.  If you have to have an account that is of a certain level, I'm sure someone has a friend or perhaps even -you- have a friend that is quitting EQ and doesn't want their character to go to waste because &quot;they might come back, they just don't know&quot;.   Easy.  <br>
<br>
We're all smart, hip, fabulous, intelligent people - lets act like it.<br>
